{"tid":377473,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(live)清邁原來都可以咁樣玩","createTime":"2017-08-27T17:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:22:47.000Z","uid":33240,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"57eec54f5e777becb17e827bb698d4a2d1abccac","tid":377473,"uid":33240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:18:36.000Z","msg":"Hello is me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知大家聽過清邁未呢？ 去過清邁未呢？<br />\n<br />\n前言<br />\n<br />\n毒撚開左第一個post 之後得到唔少爸打推薦要一定去清邁，本身已經bookmark 定下年去，完全無諗過咁快去多次泰的（好彩跳出曼谷了）<br />\n<br />\n事緣係某位岩岩一齊去泰國既朋友仔S同埋佢朋友T 話心郁郁想去清邁 原本我都無理到 但fb 成日彈左某個清邁旅居page 同埋三條友仔（其實係我）開個講清邁既whatsapp grp 之後變得一發不可收拾  買機票搶唔到mega sale 之後比我地搵到清邁去 清萊番既方法會平多幾百 窮撚就1號番黎 跟著4號就開sem <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就開始長達半年既實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋真的真的，d 人講清邁係一個好岩hea 遊慢活既地方，可能自己比太多internal 既壓力自己，所以六七月耳鳴得好緊要，希望去清邁都可以幫自己放鬆，黎個真正既休息。 係半年應該幾辛苦既實習之前，休息後搵番小小動力繼續為自己加油。 <br />\n<br />\n嘻前言就講完了，踏上去清邁既旅程了！<br />\n<br />\n打完依篇之後,一直都mon 住UO 去CN d flight ，原來長期dealy 無下限既依排進步左，再點知黎多過帕卡 <br />\n<br />\n但好彩都有得飛 :0) <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地到清邁之後係酒店擺底少少野，原來諗著Sunday Night Market 但已經趕唔到（9點幾先settle 好而十點半就night market bye bye 左）<br />\n<br />\n咁點算好呢，清邁都幾早收檔。 <br />\n<br />\n佢就帶我地住個頭附近既一間local 餐廳食野。<br />\n起初落車心諗佢會唔會好似曼谷d 的士司機同d 垃圾黑店夾好咁 但唔係個會事黎 食左一餐都算唔錯既第一餐 起碼幫驚左成個星期颱風既我地定下驚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011211_f04f48f5c4977a5f0cae8ba7aefde160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011211_f04f48f5c4977a5f0cae8ba7aefde160.jpg&h=eceb524c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011215_5d7da382ef3a48f457d4059eb782e7f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011215_5d7da382ef3a48f457d4059eb782e7f9.jpg&h=bb7171c3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011217_50b025bb217c6032e96aa3f1dd16ca73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011217_50b025bb217c6032e96aa3f1dd16ca73.jpg&h=a7c1f512&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011222_29624c147c622124d0eebb7d7f228573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011222_29624c147c622124d0eebb7d7f228573.jpg&h=8063e8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你知架啦，充滿蛇仔字既地方見到中文（殘體）會有少驚，但三個人食左都多野再加啤酒係千5bahts 到，抵屌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用甘蔗（都算係啦）既價錢食到鵝肝既野食，依個應該係中意泰國其中一個原因<br />\n叫左既菜裡面，咖哩炒蟹肉同檸檬爐魚都好正，兩個都少貴（390B,90幾hkd)但係值既，香港都要用390蚊 ......港幣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兩個送飯送啤酒一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTom yum kung 同som tam 係重口味人之必食！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011536_3c3949acb13347a0ff6e40c72ac3ea3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011536_3c3949acb13347a0ff6e40c72ac3ea3e.jpg&h=8214c946&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011537_dd4587d0c07616b6a1f1ee283b680148.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011537_dd4587d0c07616b6a1f1ee283b680148.jpg&h=be205c86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011539_7447d9b5891831020916a4026e5e89dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011539_7447d9b5891831020916a4026e5e89dd.jpg&h=902174cc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011541_3a8312d62d7a9be13b0e87422eda443a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011541_3a8312d62d7a9be13b0e87422eda443a.jpg&h=313e6065&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/28/011542_1095d79f1a2f07db9a787c19a053d6d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F28%2F011542_1095d79f1a2f07db9a787c19a053d6d5.jpg&h=540fcf7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"008f3e1c686be5aabf5d1250c2e528de073efdbf","tid":377473,"uid":40575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"鳩hea真係一流"},{"pid":"27a208a118593349629d6f929c8a371ba4e5e9ef","tid":377473,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T19:13:27.000Z","msg":"聽日去 留名"},{"pid":"0aec224b9576897e1bc353795333bff988b9467d","tid":377473,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T05:42:01.000Z","msg":"係清邁LM"},{"pid":"9d3bf81fbee931c208572ffaf519a25f7447592b","tid":377473,"uid":33240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"偷偷地推下post 先<br />\n今日算係黎到清邁第三日 但聽日就要起程去清萊<br />\n係依幾日我既生活係食野 按摩 食野 影相 同按摩 <br />\n真係好鬼疏乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今晚會upload 我覺得泰國裡面 清邁裡面 都真係幾好食 抵屌既餐廳"},{"pid":"09a6c876da5be25884e3f34983b98d53d0eedcdb","tid":377473,"uid":33240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"Cafe de nimman -可能係岩哂咩都想試d 既你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旅伴講泰國通胡xx 講過一句說話，話清邁好食既餐廳通常都係巷仔入面。 <br />\n依句說話聽落廢廢地，但都算幾岩黎形容 Cafe de nimman。<br />\n<br />\nCafe de nimman 仲要係曾經2011 年評過係泰國最好既餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然唔知點解宜家無繼續有依個榮譽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但曾經即係都表示佢都起碼係有實力既～聽個名會覺得同cafe de coral 係同一個層次類別咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但真心推介比去清邁既爸打絲打試下。 因為我未試過24小時內番炒多次同一間野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要真係仲覺得好食既！<br />\n<br />\n尼曼區好西真係好多，但匯集道道野食有驚喜 正正常常既可能都要再等大家搵下。<br />\n<br />\n依個餐廳有簡簡單單既泰北菜、fushion 菜，但每一樣都交出左佢應有既味道，環境唔錯，極力推介比大家hehe<br />\n<br />\n環境黎講同thonglor 區d 貴野西餐有得揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都多泰國人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然第二日食都有香港人 不過奇怪餐廳真係幾唔錯 但唔算好多生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/010541_fbcf15d8b505bea03feb58d66cfab357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F010541_fbcf15d8b505bea03feb58d66cfab357.jpg&h=5587abdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/010543_f1fc5d05bc325cfb4c31eae74d38582d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F010543_f1fc5d05bc325cfb4c31eae74d38582d.jpg&h=956cc87d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/010544_540df027ce72d560839f88312f578c45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F010544_540df027ce72d560839f88312f578c45.jpg&h=39e36b78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/010546_5a772c893368735b5ddfd2a6d345b209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F010546_5a772c893368735b5ddfd2a6d345b209.jpg&h=2b7295fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/010548_13c37c69e266365aab354617008429d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F010548_13c37c69e266365aab354617008429d6.jpg&h=ad73d37c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好貼心仲會比坐室外既客人蚊怕水～係體貼既～<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/010929_f2ace1acdb3a47485710d5810a7f11ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F010929_f2ace1acdb3a47485710d5810a7f11ad.jpg&h=86fef22b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011104_329e6d822b2ecbdba4d125bf7326bccc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011104_329e6d822b2ecbdba4d125bf7326bccc.jpg&h=55f14ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011106_54a71f97b0f6cb06e699b5b84a18f353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011106_54a71f97b0f6cb06e699b5b84a18f353.jpg&h=4d7caf62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011108_4a14b6ed19dfec6aa2be3ec259ae6713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011108_4a14b6ed19dfec6aa2be3ec259ae6713.jpg&h=d2b1dedd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011109_5df720ef60a14f5fe6f1f70d2bd5350d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011109_5df720ef60a14f5fe6f1f70d2bd5350d.jpg&h=f3e19d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011110_652ed1941ffad1ef598036721daf3360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011110_652ed1941ffad1ef598036721daf3360.jpg&h=0611db17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011201_e019d42f9e5b475018a1d97bbb33a4a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011201_e019d42f9e5b475018a1d97bbb33a4a3.jpg&h=6f0d386d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011203_a2a2da2f1baee8996d3cea7648392039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011203_a2a2da2f1baee8996d3cea7648392039.jpg&h=f5ce0441&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011204_fbbf8db3a1b8c7441fdaada17575d95d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011204_fbbf8db3a1b8c7441fdaada17575d95d.jpg&h=b5e67ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011206_f4a9ee3759689ef52919a6d0b352492b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011206_f4a9ee3759689ef52919a6d0b352492b.jpg&h=1e7679d4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011208_2b0925c0a7ce24e011ad2cff67f4e097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011208_2b0925c0a7ce24e011ad2cff67f4e097.jpg&h=067925fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心值得推介係羅勒炒德國豬手，豬手好入味，羅勒好似紫菜而兩樣野mix 埋一齊係出奇地好食。 旅伴兩個都好中意生蝦，係囉，食到一條都大隻有肉唔腥既生蝦係香港都幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好難得既係有泰北E san Salad ，E san 係泰北一個民族而佢地既野食幾難搵，我係曼谷食過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係好打拗d 肉粒洋蔥夾著生菜咁食的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冬蔭功之前都聽過介紹好大碗 真係好大碗 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  三個人先岩岩好ko<br />\n同埋香蕉煎餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為好食既關係，第二日係古城西北按完摩後諗唔到食咩，就番去再食多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好食再order 豬手同生蝦<br />\n<br />\nSom Tam 好大份好多好正！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011832_f43f432605535763e597145a3cac87c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011832_f43f432605535763e597145a3cac87c1.jpg&h=6724362f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011834_62b08a68c8bf1ade68ff5b8cc8cefe34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011834_62b08a68c8bf1ade68ff5b8cc8cefe34.jpg&h=4099540a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011836_de7217c754778a9f23042984d2021a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011836_de7217c754778a9f23042984d2021a3c.jpg&h=6401427d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011837_6fe47cb22560085ff8a8fe7f40b66f53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011837_6fe47cb22560085ff8a8fe7f40b66f53.jpg&h=4b6a1cee&s={SIZE}\" />[img]<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011839_f01ddb22805f6641b023616cdd33e2e3.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F31%2F011839_f01ddb22805f6641b023616cdd33e2e3.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=cEEDOG%2F6rFowkRfuFgteHrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=dc44f5b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/31/011839_f01ddb22805f6641b023616cdd33e2e3.jpg[/img</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重點黎喇，我地食左幾多錢呢？<br />\n佢d 野算係清邁黎講都叫貴貴地，但咁既環境咁既食物（我同旅伴x2都每次叫左7 樣野食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 食物質素真唔伏 大約每人80~90hkd"},{"pid":"0f61e937d7a5a017de6a37836478f2ab207aa6c1","tid":377473,"uid":122699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T18:48:52.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n<br />\n我都想睇下屋企附近有乜玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023acb4ac44deb7f0cbafa7ec1f6c2972a6bc7f3","tid":377473,"uid":43956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T22:39:43.000Z","msg":"留阿名<br />\n我過多排都去 可唔可以講多d  第一次去泰"},{"pid":"2386a737143d0cd809ec8af9d1e25d7067010494","tid":377473,"uid":73804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:22:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSUELQq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSUELQq.png&h=0aa38976&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n要求：識外語 經驗不拘 最好喺外國 唔喺都唔拘"}]}